", "recommendations/2/date": "July 3, 2013", "recommendations/2/description": "I had the pleasure to work with Natacha at the Sheraton Hotel in Moorea, French Polynesia  for over a year.\nIn her role she was the executive assistant of the GM than later expanded her role to become  Human resources Manager. During the Pre-opening period in particular Natacha was very  committed to her work and although she was not directly reporting to me was involved in several joint projects  in the preparation phase of the property.\nI have no hesitation to recommended Natacha as a very dedicated and hardworking person.", "recommendations/2/name": "Natacha B.", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "National Contract Administrator", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/natacha-b-2433074a/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAApeNJMBTYfJ-iUaO3kMUFYuH9dL3UFq6SI", "recommendations/3/context": "Luca managed Nasrulla directly", "recommendations/3/date": "May 8, 2011", "recommendations/3/description": "During his time at the property, I had the pleasure to collaborate with Nasrulla. Originally his mandate with us was on a task force assignment from a sister property which later developed into a longer consultancy period. Nasrulla always showed true commitment and passion for his job in completing the tasks assigned to him, being both a great trainer and a detailed orientated Housekeeping professional.\nWhilst his induction was challenging due to the location of the property and the integration with a culturally diverse team,   Nasrulla succeeded in strengthening the department and delivered excellent service. \n I have no hesitation to recommend Nasrulla and wish him all the success he deserves.", "recommendations/3/name": "Nasrulla Ali", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "General Manager", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nasrulla-ali-3549681b/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAQ8OfABcuhM1rnKQ9HnKsLHyjO04wZvgQA", "skills/0/titl